{"pid":"aa454070f3e02c725d77027bd1ec5a9b683ee91d","tid":2148463,"uid":226073,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T04:57:37.000Z","msg":"快啲放棄香港，去英國啦。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T05:05:25.000Z","msg":"仲走到，未係極權國家。"},{"pid":"591536d66a82a0581cd4abe6b45e14830e5ac20b","tid":2148463,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T05:07:25.000Z","msg":"昏迷左幾多年"},{"pid":"3370794eda4bf67cc35a7432d1ac71ec72f9676d","tid":2148463,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T05:08:19.000Z","msg":"人善人欺"},{"pid":"4d802207bbecc44a6b76f6f3e8c5c9ccc4e921f7","tid":2148463,"uid":97776,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T05:09:22.000Z","msg":"police state咗好耐"},{"pid":"074625761431fbb2c1bcf97d0b537670a13f1ead","tid":2148463,"uid":263648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ec225cc7306d1e65d22181f7136285a838fe599a","tid":2148463,"uid":133817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T02:53:29.000Z","msg":"只係差到行埋全民監察<br />\n你開間報紙話下政府就係顛覆國家<br />\n你開間舖頭貼下poster又係顛覆<br />\n做政治人物會可能俾人長期係樓下望住<br />\n學生答條歷史題目又係傷害國家感情<br />\n上下當地論壇竟然係傾點離開呢到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T05:14:32.000Z","msg":"似係1930-1938年之間的納粹時代，在1935年剛通過咗《紐倫堡法案》，合法迫害緊猶太人，又未到1938年熱戰奧地利之前。<br />\n<br />\n呢個階段 --&gt; <br />\n&quot;<em>1933年4月初德國在地方和國家的層面上都界定猶太人的地位與權利。1935年剝奪猶太人基本權利的《紐倫堡法案》象徵着德國反猶立法的高峰。納粹黨員亦以剝奪財富、禁止跨族通婚、禁止從事某些職業（如法官、醫生或教師等）的方式對猶太人進行迫害。而後納粹黨開始宣傳「猶太人不適合處在德國的社會中」，並以此為由不斷在各個領域加劇對猶太人的矮化，其他德國百姓也對此逐漸麻木，這一切最終發展成為猶太人大屠殺。而對於不支持反猶主義的德國人，或是公開作出任何不符納粹宣傳行為的人，都會被蓋世太保所監視，他們的合法權利將被剝奪，甚至會被送入集中營[37]。在納粹德國，幾乎一切的人和物都被統治者監視着。納粹黨最初運用各種暴力或非暴力手段奪得政權，然後再通過操縱議會通過各類法案擴大權力，利用警力和自身的武裝力量得以滲透全國，最終將權力延伸到國家和地方的所有機關，使該黨在短時間內排除異己，迅速壟斷德國的政權，控制國家的方方面面&quot;</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E7%B4%8D%E7%B2%B9%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E7%25B4%258D%25E7%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25Yq9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=4493d2be\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E7%B4%8D%E7%B2%B9%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B</a>"},{"pid":"dbe0741f86670aa9b9bdc0ab581d93ec1679a5bd","tid":2148463,"uid":311198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T05:19:43.000Z","msg":"Since the beginning of time la <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc7a6ecb999196e1ae896ab7ca02f74657aba911","tid":2148463,"uid":19990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T07:27:24.000Z","msg":"係，咁可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 移民嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f72ea1c1e49c6c10b34e0efa2e86e1b997a81b","tid":2148463,"uid":353714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T07:30:52.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係"},{"pid":"6418f07d77068cc9409b2dfaec8d95dcf315c762","tid":2148463,"uid":133817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc7a6ecb999196e1ae896ab7ca02f74657aba911","tid":2148463,"uid":19990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T07:27:24.000Z","msg":"係，咁可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 移民嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T12:13:52.000Z","msg":"宜家既狀態都係等sir this way"},{"pid":"b5ee3b88ccc413ceb8408f3b1c0924ecbf5c68ab","tid":2148463,"uid":103050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T12:15:38.000Z","msg":"本來係傀儡獨裁政權<br />\n一年前變左極權"},{"pid":"c822318666d67c72c30ef425da21de8bc8772b0e","tid":2148463,"uid"